gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 111, Jazz 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Jazz, 111-95. Nikola Jokic recorded 28 points, 13 rebounds, and seven assists for the Nuggets, while Jamal Murray added 28 points, four assists, and four steals in the victory. Talen Horton-Tucker tallied 24 points, three rebounds, and two assists for the Jazz in the loss. The Nuggets improve to 55-24, while the Jazz fall to 29-50.
